<p begin="00:01:57.518" end="00:02:03.757" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I PLAYED THE MAN WHO REALLY DID </span><span style="block">WRITE AND DIRECT "DEEP THROAT" </span><span style="block">AND HE REALLY DID HAVE A PIECE--</span></p>


