<p begin="00:02:37.524" end="00:02:40.961" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; IT MADE AN UNBELIEVABLE </span><span style="block">AMOUNT OF MONEY.</span></p>

<p begin="00:02:40.961" end="00:02:49.336" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I GUESS THEN CAME "DEBBIE DOES </span><span style="block">DALLAS" AND "BEYOND THE GREEN </span><span style="block">DOOR." </span><span style="block">AND POOR LINDA LOVELACE NEVER</span></p>



