<p begin="00:03:10.057" end="00:03:15.128" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">BUT TODAY, THEY-- I DON'T BEEN </span><span style="block">BACKEND, BUT THEY DO-- THEY GET </span><span style="block">HIGHLY PAID.</span></p>


