<p begin="00:03:16.864" end="00:03:20.968" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; John: THE CLEVER THING </span><span style="block">ABOUT THIS MOVIE IT'S THE SAME </span><span style="block">STORY TOLD TWICE.</span></p>


<p begin="00:03:20.968" end="00:03:25.906" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">YOU GET THE GLAMMUOUS VERSION OF </span><span style="block">IT FOR THE FIRST HALF OF THE </span><span style="block">FILM WHEN IT IS FUNNY, IN WHICH</span></p>


<p begin="00:03:25.906" end="00:03:30.344" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">ARE YOU APPEAR AND THE SECOND </span><span style="block">HALF YOU GET THE REALITY OF WHAT </span><span style="block">YOU'VE JUST SEEN, WHICH WAS </span><span style="block">APPALLING.</span></p>



<p begin="00:03:30.344" end="00:03:30.844" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; HORRIBLE.</span></p>
