<p begin="00:03:36.650" end="00:03:37.918" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">RESPECTED IN ANY HUMAN FORM.</span></p>
<p begin="00:03:37.918" end="00:03:42.556" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; NO, AND WHEN SHE CAME FORWARD </span><span style="block">TO REVEAL THAT SHE GOT A LOT OF </span><span style="block">CRAP FOR THAT, TOO.</span></p>


<p begin="00:03:42.556" end="00:03:51.365" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">YOU KNOW, THE WAY SHE ACTUALLY </span><span style="block">PUT IT WAS, "EVERY TIME YOU SEE </span><span style="block">ME HAVING SEX ON SCREEN IN 'DEEP</span></p>


<p begin="00:03:51.365" end="00:03:54.668" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THROAT' I WAS BEING RAPED." </span><span style="block">THAT'S THE WAY SHE FELT ABOUT </span><span style="block">IT.</span></p>


<p begin="00:03:54.668" end="00:03:56.103" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">IT WAS A HARD TIME FOR HER.</span></p>
<p begin="00:03:56.103" end="00:03:59.540" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I HAVE NEVER SEEN A MOVIE </span><span style="block">STRUCTURED THE WAY YOU JUST </span><span style="block">MENTIONED.</span></p>


