<p begin="00:04:06.713" end="00:04:08.081" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; THAT'S THE INTERESTING THING.</span></p>
<p begin="00:04:08.081" end="00:04:09.850" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">IT SAYS YOU ENJOYED THAT STORY?</span></p>
<p begin="00:04:09.850" end="00:04:12.319" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">GUESS WHAT, YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE </span><span style="block">DONE.</span></p>

<p begin="00:04:12.319" end="00:04:13.820" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">LET'S LOOK AT THE REALITY OF IT.</span></p>
<p begin="00:04:13.820" end="00:04:20.060" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">IT MAKES YOU COMPLICITY IN WHAT </span><span style="block">YOU JUST HAVE BEEN-- WHETHER </span><span style="block">TITULATED OR ENJOYED IT, IT</span></p>


